Properties.Name: Text
Properties.Value: This Workflow retrieves business partner data from SAP S/4HANA, checks if each partner has already been processed, and then maps and creates new Salesforce Accounts for unprocessed partners. Successes and errors are logged using key-value pairs for tracking integration status.

Properties.Name: Description
Properties.Value: Retrieves general data fields of all the business partner records available in the system.

Name: SAP S/4HANA Business Partner To Salesforce Account
Description: This Workflow retrieves business partner data from SAP S/4HANA, checks if each partner has already been processed, and then maps and creates new Salesforce Accounts for unprocessed partners. Successes and errors are logged using key-value pairs for tracking integration status.
